    <string name="readme_content" tools:ignore="MissingTranslation"><![CDATA[
    \n\n<b>PROJECT DESCRIPTION</b>\n\n
    Welcome to the Task Manager App application, a task manager designed to help you organize and stick to your daily commitments.
    \n\nThis Android application allows users to create, modify, and track their tasks efficiently.
    \n\n<b>KEY FEATURES</b>\n
    \u2022 Task Addition: Quick creation of new tasks (via the FAB button).\n
    \u2022 Editing & Deletion: Updating and removal of existing tasks.\n
    \u2022 Task Filtering: Distinct viewing of completed tasks and to-do tasks.\n
    \u2022 Reminders: Association of a time and due date with each task.\n
    \u2022 Calendar Integration: Option to add a task as a reminder in the native calendar.
    \n\n<b>TECHNICAL INFORMATION</b>\n
    \u2022 Platform: Android\n
    \u2022 Language: Kotlin\n
    \u2022 Architecture: MVVM
    \n\n<b>DEVELOPMENT TEAM</b>\n
    \u2022 Developer: Chloe DAUNAS\n
    \u2022 Developer: Marina Vanita FOUODJO NGNITEDEMO\n
    \u2022 Developer: Andi (B. A.) RODRIGUEZ MACUACE\n
    \u2022 Developer: Monisha CLEMENCEAU\n\n
]]></string>
